1. Konfigurasi Kredensial (Username & Password)
Kita masukkan akun nicfi ke dalam database client Cisco.
conf t
crypto ikev2 client-authentication eap
 user nicfi password nicfi$001#
exit

2. Konfigurasi IKEv2 Profile (Otak Koneksi)
crypto ikev2 profile FORTI-PROFILE
 match identity remote address 103.52.213.10 255.255.255.255
 identity local email nicfi@vpn.com  # Identitas lokal formal
 authentication local eap-client     # Cisco bertindak sebagai client
 authentication remote pre-share     # Fortinet pakai PSK
 keyring local FORTI-KEY
 dpd 10 3 on-demand
exit

3. Konfigurasi Interface Tunnel
Interface ini akan mencoba menghubungi Fortinet secara otomatis.
interface Tunnel1
 description LINK-TO-FORTINET-HQ
 ip unnumbered GigabitEthernet8
 ip mtu 1400
 ip tcp adjust-mss 1360
 tunnel source GigabitEthernet8
 tunnel destination 103.52.213.10
 tunnel mode ipsec ipv4
 tunnel protection ipsec profile FORTI-VTI-PROFILE
exit

4. Langkah Krusial: NAT-Traversal
crypto ipsec nat-transparency udp-encapsulation

